{
    //**********
    // M A I L
    //**********
    "ES_IntroMail": "Hi farmer!^My name's Eloise, and my father and I live in a neighborhood called East Scarp. There's a beach, and a pond, and loads of berries!^My dad's a vet, and you're a farmer, so I think you two will be friends. I hope we can be friends too.^You should come visit us sometimes. But not on a school day... because then I'm in class with Jas and Vinny!^Hope to see you soon!^Eloise.",
    "ES_IntroMail.Title": "A letter from Eloise",
    "strings.lexi.CS101": "Oh! Please not touch that. Was gift from Mother!$2", //Lexi
    "MEEPLetter": "^^^   Lilith Sheridan      ^   co 1 Cherry Heights      ^   East Scarp      ^   Pelican Town      ^   Stardew Valley 5787      ^^",
    "AideenFlowerRequest": "Dear @,^I have need of assistance: My supplier has suffered most dire circumstances and is unable to supply my latest order.^I absolutely MUST have the following flowers: a sweet pea, a tulip and a blue jazz. If you could please bring them to my house at the earliest possible convenience. I would be eternally grateful - and in your debt, ^Thank you, Aideen",
    "AideenFlowerRequest.Title": "Aideen's Request",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsSpring": "Dear @,^It really would be most advantageous if I were able to source my flowers locally. Perhaps would you care to plant these for me?, ^Thank you,^Aideen.",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsSpring.Title": "Spring seeds from Aideen",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsSummer": "Dear @,^It really would be most advantageous if I were able to source my flowers locally. Perhaps would you care to plant these for me?, ^Thank you,^Aideen.",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsSummer.Title": "Summer seeds from Aideen",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsFall": "Dear @,^It really would be most advantageous if I were able to source my flowers locally. Perhaps would you care to plant these for me?, ^Thank you,^Aideen.",
    "AideenSendsFlowerSeedsFall.Title": "Fall seeds from Aideen",
    "Aideen_10HeartInvite": "Dear @,^I have heard rumors of a most mysterious and beautiful flower that grows deep in the mountains, and I was wondering if you would care to join me on an expedition!^Please, meet me at my house tomorrow morning.^^Kindest regards, Aideen. ",
    "Aideen_10HeartInvite.Title": "Aideen's Invitation.",
    "JacobDinnerDate": "Hi farmer @!^I just wanted to write and say that I really like you lots, and you should come over for dinner tomorrow night! What do you think? Dinner is at 6!^I really really hope you'll come!^ With love,^Jacob XXOO.",
    "JacobDinnerDate.Title": "Invitation to Dinner",
    "CryptoToday_Oliver": "@! We need to talk. It's about Lexi. I screwed up. I'm sorry! Meet me at the Inn.    - Oliver",
    "CryptoToday_Oliver.Title": "Urgent Letter from Oliver",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_Kale": "Howdy @!^^Hope the farm's coming along nicely and you're not working yourself too hard.^^I've got a little favor to ask: If you happen to be growing any kale, would you be able to bring me some, please? Three bunches would be great! I'm trying to master Nonna's spanakopita.^Regards, Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_Kale_name": "Rosa Requests Kale",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_Amaranth": "Howdy @!^Fall must be a busy season for you, so I hope you're not wearing yourself out.^^Small favor to ask, if I may? If you happen to have any amaranth, could you bring me some please? Three bunches. Yep, I'm still working on that spanakopita, and I heard amaranth might work for spinach.^Regards, Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_Amaranth_name": "Rosa Requests Amaranth",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_GoatCheese": "Howdy @!^^I don't suppose you happen to have any goats on your farm, do you? I'd really like to try some fresh goat cheese, if you could drop some on over, please?^^Regards, Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_Ingredients_GoatCheese_name": "Rosa Requests Goat Cheese",
    "Mail.Rosa_Recipe_Baklava": "Howdy @!^^We've known each other for a while now, so I thought I'd share a special sweet treat with you! I've modified my pappa's recipe for baklava and I thought you might like the recipe. It uses local ingredients!^^Regards, Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_gift": "Howdy @!^^I got a little too carried away with my baking - again - and thought I'd share some with my friendly not-so neighbors.^^Enjoy!^^Regards, Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_gift_name": "A Gift From Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_Recipe_Baklava_name": "Rosa's Baklava Recipe",
    "ES_Rosa10HeartMail": "Howdy @,^You are invited to a picnic by the sea!^Join us at dusk on East Scarp's foreshore, to enjoy a taste of Josa and watch the sun set over the Gem Sea.^Regards,Rosa^^Will be postponed if it's raining!",
    "ES_Rosa10HeartMail.Title": "Invition to a Twilight Picnic",
    "Josephine_GiftMailed1": "Dear @,^^I do hope farming life is treating you well, and you are not working yourself too hard!^^Whilst volunteering at a local artisan market - it is important to help where one can - I stumbled upon this pretty little trinket. I do hope you enjoy it.^^Warmest regards, Josephine",
    "Josephine_GiftMailed1.Title": "Vase From Josephine",
    "JulietInvitationToSeance": "Hey @, the Kat's Away gang have a little surprise planned for our uninvited guest. You wanna come join the fun? Come to Scarp Inn after 8pm. Be there and experience a real taste of the supernatural.^^Love, Jules.^^PS: Not a literal taste, although there may be some spirits!",
    "JulietInvitationToSeance.title": "Invitation to ???",
    "Kataryna_Junkmail": "Is there something weird in your neighborhood? Cryptozoology Today seeks sightings of the mysterious, the magical, the supernatural.^^For reports, submissions, inquiries or subscriptions, call XXX-XXXX. No story is too strange.",
    "Kataryna_Junkmail.title": "Cryptozoology Today Flyer",
    "Kataryna_voidegg": "I've been talking chickens with Shane - absolutely droll, I know - and he mentioned he'd once found a strange black egg in the coop. He suggested that you might know about them. Do you? I'd pay decent coin for one!^^Ciao, Kataryna",
    "Kataryna_voidegg.title": "Kataryna's Void Egg Request",
    "kataryna_voidegghatching": "@!!!^^Ms. Kataryna has bought us the weirdest egg! Its black and red and we're incubating it for her. She thinks its a monster! I hope it isn't. Unless maybe its a dragon, that'd be wicked!^^Dad says its gonna hatch in about 5 days! Come see us then.^^Love, Eloise <",
    "kataryna_voidegghatching.title": "Eloise About An Egg",
    "EloisePuppyInvite": "Dear @!!^Nana's invited me to a charity adoption event in Chestervale! She said I could bring a friend! So I thought I'd ask you! There's going to be lots and lots of dogs! Do you like dogs???!! It's on the weekend. Please come!^Love Eloise < ^^PS: Meet outside our house at 10!^This weekend!",
    "EloisePuppyInvite.Title": "Invitation from Eloise",
    "Vivienne_LetterInvite": "Hello @, ^Remember the old orchard to the east? Can you meet with me and some others there around noon, please.^Nothing shady! Just some of those loose ends that need tying up, and I'd like you to bear witness.^    -Vivienne Trenton",
    "Vivienne_LetterInvite.Title": "Vivienne's Invitation",
    "Mail.Eloise_Recipe_CheesyJellyToast": "Hi farmer!^I've decided to send you my favoritist recipe in the whole wide world! It's really, really, really good. All you need is bread and cheese and jelly. I like strawberry the best. And proper cheese.. not goat cheese, that's icky.^^Dad slices the bread for me, because he says I massiker it but I'm sure you'll be fine. And make sure you use heaps of jelly!^^Love, Eloise.",
    "Mail.Eloise_CheesyJellyToast_name": "How to make Cheesy Jelly Toast!",
    "passedOut.mail": "Hey @,^Hope you're feeling better. Please try not to take a nap in the wilderness again! Something could've eaten you, and then I'd never have forgiven myself!^Rosa",
    "passedOut.mail.name": "Note from Rosa",
    "passedOut.mailEyvind": "Hey @,^I hope you got home safely. It's weird, but I found you on the doorstep when I went out to check the mail. Odd place to take a nap. Look after yourself!^Rosa",
    "juliet_invite": "Hey babe!^Guess what? The powers-that-be have granted me parole, and there's someone in Grampleton I've gotta talk to.^No pressure, but if you could come along and hold my hand - metaphorically or literally! - I could really use the company.^I'll be headed out after 5 pm, if you want to meet me at the bus stop?^- Juliet.",
    "juliet_invite.title": "Juliet's request",
    "juliet_vet": "Hey @,^I've heard there's a vet in East Scarp, so I'm taking Gremlin there to get her checked over. Do you want to come with me? If so, meet me in his waiting room sometime within the next week. I'd appreciate it!^Regards, Jules.^^PS: I WILL go without you.",
    "juliet_vet.title": "Vet visit",
    "juliet_vetdone": "Hey @,^so, I went to the vet. Sorry you couldn't make it! His name's Jacob, and he's easy on the eye. Anyhow, Gremlin's fine. Thank Yoba. Just skinny and stuff.^He offered to find her a new home, but I've decided to keep her. Jessie loves her too.^So anyway, drop by and see us sometime.^ - Jules",
    "juliet_vetdone.title": "Vet Visit",
    "mail.Jas_Letter.title": "A letter from Jas",
    "mail.Jas_Letter.text": "Dear farmer @,^We are practicing letter writing with Miss Penny. Today I chose to write to you. I hope all is good on your farm and wish you a very happy day!^^Kind regards,^Jas^^PS: I hope you like this letter, please tell Miss Penny that I did a good job. :)^PSS: Mr Ginger says 'hi'",
    "mail.Tristan_BakedFishGift.title": "Tristan wants fish",
    "mail.Tristan_BakedFishGift.text": "Hey @,^I need your help. I'm absolutely rubbish at cooking and I want to surprise someone.^Can you rustle me up a platter of baked fish?^Meet me on the pier at noon.^^Please and thank you!^Triss",
    "mail.Tristan_MtEvermore.title": "Invite to Mt Evermore",
    "mail.Tristan_MtEvermore.text": "Hey @, want to join me on an adventure? I've always wanted to watch the sunset from the top of Mt. Evermore, and I'd love someone to keep me out of trouble.^If it's a 'yes', meet me by the stone bridge am hour before sunset and wear good walking shoes!^Yours, Tristan.",
    "mail.Wizard.Wizard_CatPicnic.title": "An Invitation",
    "mail.Wizard.Wizard_CatPicnic.text": "Greetings young adept,^ Our mutual friend requests your presence before the gaze of Old Man Cannoli, after the fall of darkness.^  M. Rasmodius, Wizard.",
    "mail.HarvestGoddess.Wizard_CatPicnic.title": "An Invitation",
    "mail.HarvestGoddess.Wizard_CatPicnic.text": "Hello, dear!^ Our mutual friend requests your presence before the gaze of Old Man Cannoli, after the fall of darkness.^  .",
    "Mail.Jade_IronBar": "Hi @!^Remember my hypothesis? I'm going to need an iron bar.^Why? Oh, fairies are allergic to iron, and I need it for my research.^Thanks!^Jade",
    "Mail.Jade_IronBar_name": "Jade requests an iron bar",
    "Mail.Jade_FairyPool": "Hi @!^Professor Jasper's told me about a really magical place, and I want to share it with you.^Meet me at the 'Troll Bridge' (that massive stone one near the silo) at noon.^(Don't worry, it's not a date it's RESEARCH).^Thanks!^Jade",
    "Mail.Jade_FairyPool_name": "Invitation from Jade",
    "Mail.Jade_10heartmail": "Hey @!^I'm headed to Zuzu tomorrow for my big presentation, and I'd really, really like to see you before I go.^Can you please come visit me tonight? It'd really mean a lot.^I'll leave the door unlocked.^ Hugs, Jade^^PS: You can bring your PJs if you want to (this *might* me a date).",
    "Mail.Jade_10heartmail_name": "Invitation from Jade",
    "Mail.Beatrice_Recipe_Curry": "Salut @,^Now that we are friends, I have decided to share a special recipe with you. This was Raoul's favorite curry - although he preferred it with more spice, this has enough kick for me!^I hope that you will enjoy it.^   Bien à vous, Beatrice",
    "Mail.Beatrice_Recipe_Curry_name": "Beatrice's Recipe",
    "Mail.Jessie_Recipe_Smoothie": "Hello @,^Need more energy in your day? Here's a recipe I rustle up to help me work long hours.^Now if only I could persuade Juliet to drink it!^^Enjoy, Jessie.",
    "Mail.Jessie_Recipe_Smoothie_name": "Jessie's Recipe",
    "Mail.Jessie_Recipe_SoothingCure": "Hello @,^Farming isn't easy work, and I'm sure you must be feeling the strain. This tonic helps to ease that; it strengthens and sooths your muscles.^^Please look after yourself.^Jessie",
    "Mail.Jessie_Recipe_SoothingCure_name": "Jessie's Recipe for Soothing Cure",
    "Mail.Tori_Recipe_BlissBalls": "Hi @,^I was thinking of you today, and decided to share this fun and easy recipe with you! They're little balls of delicious energy, and so easy to make!^^Have a great day,^   Tori!",
    "Mail.Tori_Recipe_BlissBalls_name": "Victoria's Recipe",
    "Mail.Jacob_Recipe_CandiedRoot": "Hello @,^Here's a favorite recipe of ours; it's also a surefire way to get Eloise to eat some vegetables!^It's quite sugary though, so best saved for special occasions.^Warm wishes, Jacob",
    "Mail.Jacob_Recipe_CandiedRoot.name": "Jacob's Recipe",
    "mail.MarnieSellsVoidGoats": "Dear @,^I met a rather interesting fellow today - a goatherder! He's brought down some kids for me to sell. They're a bit ... weird. Apparently the Nannies will produce milk and the Billies... shed a lot? Come and meet them! ^    -Marnie",
    "mail.MarnieSellsVoidGoats.name": "Void Goats For Sale!",
    "mail.AideenSellsNewFlowers": "Dear @,^I had the most frightfully peculiar visitor yesterday: A mountain of a man with curved horns like those of a goat! He gave me some most fascinating seeds, and promised me the most brilliant of blooms! If you wish to purchase some, I have a few onsale at our little stall. Please do drop by!^    - Aideen^^PS: Remember, I'm there Monday, Tuesday, Thursday between 11am and 2pm.",
    "mail.AideenSellsNewFlowers.name": "Aideen Sells Goatherd's Flower Seeds",
    "Mail.Tristan_YarnBombing": "Hello @,^Jas and I have been working on a little project. Come on over if you'd like a bit of a yarn. Haha, cos it's a wool-based project. Anyhow, stop by East Scarp sometime, okay?^      - Tristan",
    "Mail.Tristan_YarnBombing_name": "Invitation from Tristan",
    "Mail.Jasper_Peasbody": "Hello farmer,^We've never met, but I'm reaching out to you because I'm concerned about our mutual friend, Prof. Jasper Thomas. He's a hot-headed fanatic, and I've heard rumors that he's gone off into the caves following a 'white rabbit' - and, in all likelihood, got himself killed. Despite what I'm sure he's told you (since we parted rather unamicably), I've never wished harm upon him. But then again... he was always a bit of a stubborn fool, and never inclined to leave well alone what should be left alone!^I'm sorry, this isn't a threat! It's merely an expression of concern. Please, if you've found him - alive or dead - I'd appreciate you letting me know. Because we were friends once and, truth be told, I still care for the pig-headed fool.^^Regards, ^Professor Cameron.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Peasbody_name": "Cameron's Letter",
    "Mail.Jasper_Home": "Greetings @,^I am truly indebted to you. That you would find me, and bring me home. Or what is left of me. The infection has left me a shadow of my former self, and the injury was as dire as I feared... I hope it shall not come as too much of a shock to you, my friend.^^I shall be home tomorrow, into what Gunther has uncharitably labelled \"house arrest\". I suspect I shall achieve a great deal of writing, and possibly some reading too.^^Your company would, as always, be greatly appreciated.^^Best wishes, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Home_name": "Jasper is home.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Home1": "Dear @.^House arrest is starting to get tiresome. I miss the scent and the sound of the forest. I am becoming more adept with the wheelchair now, but alas the ground proves treacherous and uneven. I am completing my exercises every morning and evening, like a dutiful student, in the hope that soon I shall be at least somewhat mobile once more.^^Yours truly, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Home1_name": "Jasper's correspondence 1",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeA": "Greetings and salutations!^I hope things are going well for you on the farm, @, and that you are not yet weary of my correspondence. I have precious few friends in this world, and I do not wish to trouble them.^Speaking of friends - may I dare to think? - I penned a missive to Cameron and received a swift response! It appears, perhaps, that a visit may be imminent.^^Yours fondly, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeA_name": "Jasper and Cameron.",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeB_Host": "Hello @!^Apologies for my melancholic mood earlier. I find my outlook much improved, for I have just received excellent news. My wound has healed fully, thus I am to be fitted with a prosthetic. I will become bionic man! Ah, I jest, but it will be good to get back on my own two - well, one - foot again.^Anyway. I trust all is well with you, and maybe hope that one day soon I shall be able to visit your farm once more. For even though the mines may now be denied me, there is still so much of this world left to explore.^^Fare thee well, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeB_Host_name": "Jasper's Prosthetic.",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeB_Hand": "Hello @!^Apologies for my melancholic mood earlier. Memories of that night still haunt me. But I am seeing someone about them, so do not fear for me.^I trust all is well with you, and maybe hope that one day soon I shall be able to visit your farm once more. For even though the mines may now be denied me, there is still so much of this world left to explore.^^Fare thee well, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_HomeB_Hand_name": "Jasper's Melancholy.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Picnic": "My dear friend,^ I have a special place I must show you! Please meet me across the Scarp river from the silo over the noon-time period on the next sunny day. You might like to bring your swimwear!^^Fondest regards, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_Picnic_name": "Invitation to a picnic",
    "Mail.Jasper_LoveLetter": "Dearest @,^ Some have claimed I have a way with words... others that I am too flowery for my own good. I have tried to capture my feelings for you in words. Even written poetry like our friend Elliot (it was very bad, no, you cannot see it). I cannot describe how what we have makes my heart feel lighter, and my soul soar. How much the sight of your smile makes me feel alive...^I guess, what I am saying is... I love you, @.^^Yours, now and forever, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_LoveLetter_name": "A Love Letter from Jasper",
    "Mail.Gunther_Letter": "Jasper and @,^Hope all's going well for you both, and that Jasper hasn't dug up your farm looking for artifacts yet!^I'm glad that you found each other. Anyhow, I was tidying up around the place, and found something that reminded me of Jasper, so I thought he might like it.^Take care, both of you, and don't be strangers!^^Regards, Gunther.",
    "Mail.Gunther_Letter_name": "A gift from Gunther",
    "Mail.Gunther_Letter2": "Jasper and @,^Hope all is going well for you both, and that Jasper hasn't dug up your farm looking for artifacts yet!^I hear you are expecting a new family member and wanted to offer my congratulations!^^Regards Gunther.",
    "Mail.Gunther_Letter2_name": "A Letter from Gunther",
    "Mail.Jasper_BabyArrives": "Dear @,^^Might I say how delighted my father and I were to hear your news and to welcome our first grandchild into the world. We hope one day to be able to visit, but until then, we send our love - and this enormous toy.^^Love, Mom and Dad.",
    "Mail.Jasper_BabyArrives_name": "A letter from Mom and Dad",
    "Mail.Jasper_BabyCrawling": "Dear Jasper,^I know that we've had our differences in the past, but I wanted to send you my congratulations.^I cannot believe that you, a man so dedicated to his work, would settle down and become a family man.^I am pleased that you have found your happiness.^^I do miss our friendship, you know...^With my dearest regards and deepest regrets, Cameron.",
    "Mail.Jasper_BabyCrawling_name": "A letter from Cameron",
    "Mail.Jasper_Todd": "JOJA PROTEKT TODDLER GATES!^^Keep your children contained with JoJa's patented Protekt Toddler gates, guaranteed to keep the kids out of harm's way while you go about your day!^^Available now from your local JojaMart, only 1500g!",
    "Mail.Jasper_Todd_name": "Junk Mail from JoJa",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter": "Dear @ (and Jasper, of course!),^^Thank you for all the photos you've sent us. Our grandchild is certainly growing into a right little character. Sending you our love,^^Love, Mom and Dad.",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter_name": "A letter from Mom and Dad",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter2": "Dear @ (and Jasper, of course!),^^Thank you for all the photos you've sent us. Our grandchild is certainly growing into a right little character. Sending you our love,^^Love, Mom and Dad.",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter2_name": "A letter from Mom and Dad",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter3": "Dear @ and Jasper,^Congratulations on your latest family member. Sorry we are unable to come and visit, Love Mom and Dad.^",
    "Mail.Parent_Letter3_name": "Another letter from parents",
    "Mail.Jasper_MineralGift": "My dear @,^I was cleaning out my minerals collection and found this gemstone that was superfluous to my requirements but will, perhaps, be of some use to you.^^Regards, Jasper.",
    "Mail.Jasper_MineralGift_name": "A gift from Jasper",
    "Mail.ES_IntroMail2": "Dear @, ^Welcome to Pelican Town. This is just a little note to let you know that we run a wee co-operative stall over in East Scarp. On Monday, Tuesday and Thursday, Aideen sells flowers and seeds, and on Wednesday, Friday and Saturday you can purchase a small selection of seeds and home remedies from me. Pop over to see us between 11am and 2pm.^^Hope to see you soon,^Jessie.",
    "Mail.ES_IntroMail2.Title": "Advertisement for ES Stall",
    "Mail.Josephine_Recipe_ZinfazuFruit": "Hello @,^There's this little ice cream parlour near us in Zuzu that makes the most delicious ice cream. Some time ago, I talked them in to sharing the recipe for my favorite blend, and today I would like to share it with you. The exotic taste is truly exquisite, and well suited for those of us with refined taste.^Best Wishes,^Josephine.",
    "Mail.Josephine_Recipe_ZinfazuFruit_name": "Recipe from Josephine",
    "Mail.Edith_Recipe_ButtonFruitCake": "Hello @,^Here's today's recipe from our Scarp internet diary. It's a traditional family recipe so I thought you might appreciate it, as we appreciate you. Let me know how it goes!^Best wishes,^Edith Hart",
    "Mail.Edith_Recipe_ButtonFruitCake_name": "Recipe from Edith",
    "Mail.Jade_Recipe_FairyCapAmbrosia": "Hi @!^Here's a cute little dessert I like to whip up now and then. They say fairies love it!^^ Jade <",
    "Mail.Jade_Recipe_FairyCapAmbrosia_name": "Recipe from Jade",
    "Mail.Corwin_Recipe_YohoHash": "Hey @,^When you're living on board a ship, you sometimes have to throw some stuff together. We had too many potatoes and this weird fruit and ended up with this concoction. Is it a dessert or is it dinner? Who knows, but either way, it tastes bloody good.^^Corwin.",
    "Mail.Corwin_Recipe_YohoHash_name": "Recipe from Corwin",
    "Mail.Michael_Recipe_HotChoco": "Hi Pal!^Thought I'd share my specialty recipe with you - it's made with fruit, but the taste is so rich that you can fool yourself into thinking you're drinking chocolate.^Ethan loves it.^Enjoy!^Michael",
    "Mail.Michael_Recipe_HotChoco_name": "Recipe from Michael",
    "Mail.Juliet_Recipe_ChocoBun": "Hey @!^I was bored and hungry a few weeks ago, so I threw some chocofruit custard into a bread roll and it was surprisingly delicious! I think I might have invented my signature dish! Anyways, Rosie helped me refine it, and now we're sharing it with you.^Enjoy!^Your bestie, Jules.",
    "Mail.Juliet_Recipe_ChocoBun_name": "Recipe from Juliet",
    "Mail.Jasper_Recipe_GiggleSmoothie": "Hello @,^Whilst I was researching the goblins in the Blue Mire forest, they were kind enough to share some of their recipes with me. Here is one that I found particularly useful to help me through those rough mornings in the faculty! Perhaps it could help you as well? I shall warn you, however, that it is quite an acquired taste.^Fond Regards, Jasper",
    "Mail.Jasper_Recipe_GiggleSmoothie_name": "Recipe from Jasper",
    "Mail.BeatriceCorwin_InviteRaoul":"Salut @,^Corwin and I have been talking - a lot. We have decided it is time for us to bid Raoul 'adieu'. He would not like to spend his eternity on land.^Captain Roderick will collect us from the Scarp wharf on the next fine day.^^You never knew Raoul, but you have been a good friend to us both, and we would be very grateful if you were to join us.^Bien à toi, Beatrice",
    "Mail.BeatriceCorwin_InviteRaoul_name":"Invitation from Beatrice",
    "Mail.Luma_PrismaticEgg":"Hello not-so-stinky farmer friend!^Our lovely slime friends gave us this gift for you!^^What? You surprised we can write? We have many talents! You do not know the half of it.",
    "Mail.Luma_PrismaticEgg_Name":"A gift from Luma",
    "Mail.MichaeHart_Painting":"Hi there Pal!^Thanks for coming by to visit me yesterday. And... Guess what? I finished the painting and thought it might look nice on your wall - but don't feel obliged to hang it. I'm happy just knowing it's gone to a good home.^See you again soon!^Michael",
    "Mail.MichaeHart_Painting_name":"Michael's Painting",
    "Mail.DaleInviteGraduationParty":"Hello @,^Remember how I told you I was doing those papers? Well, I've finished them. Anyhow, Rosa and Edith insisted on throwing me a celebratory party at the Inn, and you're invited! Drop by around 6.^^Thanks, Dale ",
    "Mail.DaleInviteGraduationParty.name":"Invitation to Dale's Graduation Party",
    "Mail.Rosa_Rebuild_Bridge":"Howdy @,^Since Eloise's little adventure, I've been doing some thinking... what is across that stream? What happened to the orchard? I've spoken to Robin, and she thinks we can repair the bridge - we're just going to need some materials. I've attached a list.^Can you help us, please?^Thanks!^Rosa",
    "Mail.Rosa_Rebuild_Bridge.name":"Repairing the Orchard Bridge"
    
}